&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*** UHNM Employees Only ***&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clinical Director of Paediatrics at the University Hospitals of North Midlands NHS Trust Salary: 2 PAs UHNM are looking for Clinical Director of Paediatrics to help deliver the strategic and operational objectives of the Paediatric Department and to enhance our service further, the successful applicant will be a member of a team of 41 Paediatric Consultants, Associate specialists and staff grades. UHNM’s Child Health department operates over 2 main hospital sites and a number of community settings; it is a specialist centre for many specialties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will assist in providing managerial support to the Clinical Director and other members of the Senior Management Team to help in the delivery of the wide ranging strategic, operational delivery, performance, financial and governance agendas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duration of appointment: 3 years renewable Appointment: by interview&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For information and enquiries please contact Dr Pavanasam Ramesh, Clinical Director of Child Health, on 01782 675174 , e-mail Pavanasam.Ramesh@uhnm.nhs.uk or Susanne Crossley, Child health Directorate Manager, on 01782 679310, e-mail susanne.crossley@uhnm.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
